ËÙµU<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";s:552:"<p>The Triple P- Positive Parenting Program is about teaching parents a range of parenting techniques that increase parental competence and are helpful in managing child behavioural problems. The program increases the knowledge, skills and confidence of parents, and may not only assist parents with current difficulties, but also prevent children from developing some problems, such as severe behavioural, emotional and developmental problems. The design of the Triple P program allows treatment to be tailored to the needs of individual families.</p>";}